        "success": true,
        "agent_name": "coder",
        "output": {
          "code": "def get_nth_prime(n):\n    primes = []\n    num = 2\n    while len(primes) < n:\n        for i in range(2, int(num**0.5) + 1):\n            if num % i == 0:\n                break\n        else:\n            primes.append(num)\n        num += 1\n    return primes[-1]\n\nprint(get_nth_prime(10000))",
          "rationale": "Uses a trial division algorithm to find the 10,000th prime number by iterating through integers and checking for primality."
